# ---- Booking form delivery (n8n automation) ----
# The booking modal POSTs each Discovery Session request as JSON to a
# same-origin endpoint, which Caddy proxies to the n8n webhook:
#
#   https://leanhippo.io/api/book  ->  n8n webhook "booking"
#
# n8n then emails a branded confirmation to the requester and a booking
# alert to contact@leanhippo.io.
#
# Because the endpoint is same-origin, no key and no CORS config are needed.
# Override only for local previews where /api/book is not proxied, e.g.:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_BOOKING_ENDPOINT=https://n8n.leanhippo.io/webhook/booking

# NEXT_PUBLIC_BOOKING_ENDPOINT=/api/book
